txt.en: To earn this deed, you must defeat Dargnákh, the troll that was captured in Fangorn.
You have defeated Dargnákh, the troll captured in Fangorn.
Saruman's evil followers pose a deadly threat to all who revere freedom.
To earn this deed, you must defeat Huva, a follower of the White Hand.
Huva was an acolyte of Saruman, trained in the ways of magic.
